name: Gorgeous and Bright Victorian Home
neighborhood_overview: Family friendly Neighborhood, Culturally diverse Boston, Easy to Get around,  MBTA access, walk to shops, Food, Banking, Laundry.  20 mins from downtown.
description:
My place is close to restaurants and dining, art and culture, the T and public transit . This space inspires serenity and you can let your hair down and enjoy, home away from home ; its comfort, coziness, and foodie friendly gourmet kitchen. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
note: cleaning fee as applied, is subjected to change base on length of stay, 1 to 14 days $50; 15 to 30 days will be $75; for 30 days $100 and each month there after will be $100.

The space
Each bedroom has a special access to the Sun, Bright room, hardwood floors with rich colors.

Guest access
Guess will have access to kitchen living room bath and all common areas

Other things to note
While packing, dress appropriate for all seasons but be prepared for the winter.
